professional resumes and academic documents. The modified version
remains under the terms of the MIT License.

Modifications include:
- Redesigned header with dynamic, hyperlink-enabled contact info using FontAwesome.
- Multiple spacing variants (mcdowellcv_2.cls, _3.cls, _4.cls) for different content density needs.
- New sections added: Profile, Technical Experience, Projects, Certifications.
- Date and format changes to match Indian resume standards.
- Enhanced ATS compatibility and simplified use in Overleaf and LuaLaTeX environments.
- Filename changes to avoid conflict with original class.

